1. *Gubi* se u moru ljudi. (He/She gets lost in a sea of people.)
2. Nije se žurio pa je *gubio* vreme. (He/She wasn't in a hurry, so he/she was wasting time.)
3. *Gubila* je nadu da će pronaći izlaz. (She was losing hope of finding a way out.)
4. U ovom poslu često se *gubi*. (You often get lost in this job.)
5. Ona se boji da neće naći pravi put i da će se *gubiti*. (She is afraid that she won't find the right way and will get lost.)